      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Alex Collie\n### A distributed web search engine, built and operated solo\n\nFive Go microservices talking over gRPC, a from-scratch PageRank implementation, full-text search backed by PostgreSQL, and a self-hosted Kubernetes cluster with its own observability stack — this dashboard included. Every number below is live from the running system.\n\n**[search.collie.codes](https://search.collie.codes)** — try the live search engine &nbsp;·&nbsp; **[collie.codes](https://collie.codes)** — more of my work"
      }
    },
    {
